<span id="freeTextContainer9481810270677394466">This is the first play /work by Shaw that I read, and I liked it so much, even it is old written in 1905. I am going to read his other plays and novels. Well I am going to read it again and may be I will edit this review.<br/><br/>--------------------------------<br/><i>
  <b>If God Gave the Hand, Let Not Man Withold the Sword.</b>
