    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1362943301" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7847831768631402068">Read as part of my Kindle omnibus &quot;The Plays of Shaw&quot;.<br/><br/>Very witty satire about Barbara Undershaft, a major in the Salvation Army, and her family, most notably her father who owns &amp; operates a munitions factory. The debate about physical versus moral power is a bit wordy in places otherwise I might have given this a 5 star rating. Now I am off to watch the film version with Rex Harrison and Wendy Hiller...</span>
  <span id="freeText7847831768631402068" style="display:none">Read as part of my Kindle omnibus "The Plays of Shaw".<br /><br />Very witty satire about Barbara Undershaft, a major in the Salvation Army, and her family, most notably her father who owns &amp; operates a munitions factory. The debate about physical versus moral power is a bit wordy in places otherwise I might have given this a 5 star rating. Now I am off to watch the film version with Rex Harrison and Wendy Hiller...</span>
  <a data-text-id="7847831768631402068" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

